	   <tr><td colspan=2>Anyone over 200 wis (or 200 int) is already wearing Electrum Blue Diamond earrings. Those have +15 mana (I believe, I could be wrong). So let's say, I have 210 wis, and I am wearing a BD earring. I replace the BD earring with this PoS.<br><br>Wis drops to 200, resists all drop, net gain in mana? 40. 10 points for the 10 wis over 200, 15 from the BD earring. Net 40 mana and lose resists. <br><br>Who in their right mind would use this? Unless it had the effect of Flowing Thought IV (which it doesn't), I think they completely misnamed this thing.<br><br>Dik - 58 cleric<br>&nbsp;<br>I am a Dik, more or less</td></tr>
